Sigora Haiti – The Power is Yours
















































































WELCOME TO SIGORA HAITI


                OUR MISSION IS TO PROVIDE HAITI WITH ENERGY THAT IS ..                CLEAN
RELIABLE
FAIRLY-PRICED








The Green Utility
Helping people in Haiti tap the power of the sun.










CLEAN

                                Solar and wind are clean, renewable sources of energy, replacing the burning of carbon and the noise of diesel generators.
                                

 








RELIABLE

                                24/7 electricity will be a first in many parts of Haiti, and will greatly improve health, education, and safety.
                                

 








FAIRLY-PRICED

                                Pricing that is both fair and sustainable makes operating the utility and growing its scale possible.
                                

 











To show you how important electricity is in the life of a country, let me define electricity for you this way: Electricity is life.
 - Kalebe Verdieu, 44, Director of Electricité d'Haïti in Jérémie -  









ABOUT US
Sigora Haiti is a business model with a vision



Sigora Haiti started with a small dream of electrifying a clinic and has grown into a full-scale Green Utility project. Our 10-year plan is to electrify 2 million people by 2025. We connected our first customer, the Mole-Saint-Nicolas Public Health Clinic, in December 2015. In less than one year Sigora engineered, financed, and built its first microgrid system.
Today, we provide clean, reliable, and affordable power to 5,000 people under a 50-year power supplier contract with the municipality. Our 219kW solar plant is under construction, and we have ratified additional agreements to bring power to a further 135,000 people in Haiti’s Northwest region.
Sigora’s grid technology is designed to provide more than just power metering and production monitoring, it is an integrated micro-utility management system. Our proprietary Sigora Smart Meter and cloud-based API software automate account management tasks, monitor the technical and financial performance of the grid, and provide real-time data analytics and meter control, enabling Sigora to troubleshoot and address problems before they become serious.










To learn more about Sigora's grid management system and proprietary prepay meter, visit Sigora International.




